  "question_id": "9c7b5a96-dc86-4f0c-9de4-b387c3c09541",
  "short_text": "Hollow Right Angled Triangle - 4",
  "content": "Given a number `N`, write a program to print a **Hollow Right Angled Triangle** of `N` rows using pluses (`+`) and hashes (`#`).\r\n\r\nThe first line contains hashes (`#`) and the next `N - 1` lines contain pluses (`+`)\r\n\r\n```\r\n# # # # # #\r\n+       +\r\n+     +\r\n+   +\r\n+ +\r\n+\r\n```\r\n\r\n<MultiLineNote>\r\nThere is a space after every plus (`+`) and every hash (`#`).\r\n</MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Input\r\n\r\nThe input will be a single line containing an integer representing `N`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Output\r\n\r\nThe output should be `N` rows containing hashes (`#`) and pluses (`+`) as a **Hollow Right Angled Triangle** as shown in the sample output.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Explanation\r\n\r\nFor example, if the given number is `N = 6`,\r\n\r\n- Print Hashes (`#`) and Pluses (`+`) on **6** rows as shown in the given image.\r\n  - The first row contains Hashes (`#`).\r\n  - The next **5** (`6 - 1`) rows contain Pluses (`+`).\r\n\r\n<Img imageSrc='https://assets.ccbp.in/frontend/content/programming-foundations/cx-hollow-right-angled-triangle-4.png' widthPercent='65'/>\r\n\r\n<MultiLineNote>\r\nIn the given image,\r\n\r\n- The Empty box indicates two spaces (\"&nbsp;&nbsp;\").\r\n- The Hash in the box indicates hash and a space (\"# \").\r\n- The Plus in the box indicates a plus and a space (\"+ \").\r\n</MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\nThe output should be,\r\n\r\n```\r\n# # # # # #\r\n+       +\r\n+     +\r\n+   +\r\n+ +\r\n+\r\n```",
  "question_type": "CODING",
  "content_type": "MARKDOWN",
  "codes": [
    {
      "code_id": "e8dcffe3-8ebe-4d83-8273-cb2efaf8b3e0",
      "code_content": "n = int(input())\n\nfirst_row = \"# \" * n \nprint(first_row)\n\nfor i in range(1, n - 1):\n    middle_spaces_count = (2 * n) - (2 * (i + 1)) - 2\n    middle_spaces = \" \" * middle_spaces_count\n    row = \"+ \" + middle_spaces + \"+ \"\n    print(row)\n\nif(n > 1):\n    last_row = \"+\"\n    print(last_row)",
      "language": "PYTHON",
      "default_code": true
    }
  ],
